parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall, hesitate, or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or stalls when accelerating
the transmission slips or fails to engage
the vehicle loses power or acceleration
and the vehicle may jerk or shake when shifting gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the vehicle to accelerate properly can lead to accidents, especially when merging onto highways or crossing intersections.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or fails to accelerate when merging onto highways
the engine revs but the vehicle does not move
and the vehicle may stall or lose power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch can cause the vehicle to stall or hesitate, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor

and the vehicle hesitates or stalls when shifting gears.
